name: SVGFECompositeElement
description: The SVGFECompositeElement interface corresponds to the <feComposite> element.

members.name: SVGFECompositeElement.in1
members.description: An SVGAnimatedString corresponding to the in attribute of the given element.

members.name: SVGFECompositeElement.type
members.description: An SVGAnimatedEnumeration corresponding to the type attribute of the given element. It takes one of the SVG_FECOMPOSITE_OPERATOR_* constants defined on this interface.

members.name: SVGFECompositeElement.values
members.description: An SVGAnimatedNumberList corresponding to the values attribute of the given element.
